---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure — AI Select" description="How affiliate relationships work at AI Select.">
  <div class="max-w-[42rem] mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-mono font-bold mb-8">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-[#0F0F1B] leading-relaxed
      [&_h2]:text-xl [&_h2]:font-mono [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:mb-4
      [&_h2]:pb-2 [&_h2]:border-b [&_h2]:border-gray-100
      [&_a]:text-[#00B8A2] hover:[&_a]:underline
    ">
      <p class="text-lg text-[#6B7280]">Some links on AI Select are affiliate links. If you buy or subscribe after following one, Arrivau Pty Ltd may receive a commission at no additional cost to you.</p>

      <h2>Editorial independence</h2>
      <p>Commercial relationships do not determine our ratings, conclusions, or the tools we choose to cover. We apply the same testing criteria whether or not a product offers an affiliate program. A higher commission does not produce a higher score.</p>

      <h2>How links are identified</h2>
      <p>We disclose affiliate relationships in the page context and use appropriate link attributes. Prices, availability, and program terms can change, so readers should confirm current terms on the provider's website before purchasing.</p>

      <h2>No endorsement guarantee</h2>
      <p>A product's inclusion does not guarantee that it is suitable for every user. Reviews are general information, not professional, legal, financial, or security advice. Readers remain responsible for evaluating products against their own requirements.</p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>Email <a href="mailto:contact@aiselect.ai">contact@aiselect.ai</a> if you have a question about a relationship or disclosure on a specific page.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
